## 7. Exemplo de prompt para geração de imagem

```
Create a professional educational infographic for a SQL course in Brazilian Portuguese.
Topic: [TEMA DA AULA]
Style: Clean, modern, blue/purple palette, white background, technical icons
Content: [DESCREVA OS ELEMENTOS QUE DEVEM APARECER]
Format: Horizontal comparison / vertical flow / diagram with arrows
Language: All text must be in Brazilian Portuguese (PT-BR)
```
